subject: Football
lead_paragraph: Peyton Manning did not pass for more than 257 yards in any of Denver’s last four games, but the Broncos went 4-0 because of a yeoman effort by C. J. Anderson.
snippet: Peyton Manning did not pass for more than 257 yards in any of Denver’s last four games, but the Broncos went 4-0 because of a yeoman effort by C. J. Anderson.
